summary: An Ordinance transferring Two Thousand Two Hundred Thirty-five and 77/100 Dollars ($2235.77) from the General fund of the City of Seattle to Local Improvement District No. 903 Fund, for the purpose of reimbursing said Local Improvement District No. 903 Fund with the excess in the fixed estimate for the improvement of Railroad Avenue by planking the same under Ordinance No. 10,729.
